[{"kind":1,"language":"markdown","value":"## Shall we play a game?\r\n\r\n#### Direct from GitHub: Use Git functions\r\n\r\nIf you don't want to look at or copy/paste the code, you can use Git functions in SAS to bring the program into your SAS session and play. (Requires SAS 9.4 Maint 6 or later, or SAS Viya)\r\n","outputs":[]},{"kind":2,"language":"sas","value":"options dlcreatedir;\r\n%let repopath=%sysfunc(getoption(WORK))/wordle-sas;\r\nlibname repo \"&repopath.\";\r\ndata _null_;\r\n    rc = gitfn_clone( \r\n      \"https://github.com/sascommunities/wordle-sas\", \r\n      \"&repoPath.\" \r\n    \t\t\t); \r\n    put 'Git repo cloned ' rc=; \r\nrun;\r\n%include \"&repopath./wordle-sas.sas\";\r\n\r\n","outputs":[]},{"kind":1,"language":"markdown","value":"### Already got the code? %include from here.","outputs":[]},{"kind":2,"language":"sas","value":"/* Change this path to point to your local file */\r\n%include \"path-to-code/wordle-sas.sas\";","outputs":[]},{"kind":1,"language":"markdown","value":"### Start a game\r\n\r\nThis picks a random word from the possible puzzle words.","outputs":[]},{"kind":2,"language":"sas","value":"%startGame;","outputs":[]},{"kind":1,"language":"markdown","value":"### Submit a guess","outputs":[]},{"kind":2,"language":"sas","value":"/* The start word of a genius */\r\n%guess(CRANE);","outputs":[]}]